OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith some patchy rain or drizzle. This
OL,7,Fafternoon will be dry with some
OL,8,Fsunshine breaking through at times.
OL,9,FBecoming warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry this evening with some
OL,12,Flate sunshine in the south and east.
OL,13,FThen becoming cloudy overnight with
OL,14,Fthe chance of a little drizzle in the
OL,15,Fnorth and west.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAfter a cloudy start it
OL,18,Fwill be a dry day with some sunshine
OL,19,Ffor the afternoon. Very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
